Popular Nollywood child star-turned-billionaire wife Regina Daniels has been hospitalised. The actress is back to the hospital weeks after she underwent successful surgery for an undisclosed ailment. The mother of one updated fans on the state of her health via her Snapchat story She showed off a fully bandaged wrist and captioned it “Man Down”. Although Regina Daniels did not reveal the reason for her being admitted, her fans have been sending in their good messages. In April, the 20-year-old movie star underwent surgery for an undisclosed medical condition. The movie star had taken to her Snap chat to share a video of herself being rolled to the theatre for the operation. The video also captured her billionaire husband, Ned Nwoko as he accompanied his young wife for her surgery.